<item>
            <title>[LU-8919] Move to new kernel documentation API</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8919</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The linux kernel is moving away from DocBook to Sphinx style. Lustre will need to move to this style. Information about this Doc API  can be found at &lt;a href=&quot;http://kernel.readthedocs.io/en/latest/kernel-documentation.html#sphinx-build&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://kernel.readthedocs.io/en/latest/kernel-documentation.html#sphinx-build&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="42296">LU-8919</key>
            <summary>Move to new kernel documentation API</summary>
